============
INTRODUCTION
============

test_map646 is an application to test map646's 4to6 address transration and
6to6 address transration.
Two programs are included in test_map646, test_map646_server and test_map646_client.sh.
test_map646_client is for a client, test_map646_server.sh is for a server
(in a pure IPv6 network).

test_map646 checks map646's transration using PING[V6], TCP and UDP.

==============
HOW TO COMPILE
==============

Just type 'make' in both directry, test_map646/client and test_map646/server.

==========
HOW TO USE
==========

Before running test_map646, don't forget to configure and run map646.

- for server-side
#test_map646_server <Server Port>

- for client-side
#test_map646_client.sh <V4 Server Addr> <V6 Server Addr> <Server Port>


